Detailed Description

Listener for Tunnel interface events. The abstract functions are the callback functions that is called for the respective asynchronous function call in TunnelInterface.

Implement a sub class of TunnelListener and add as a listener to the TunnelInterface to start getting tunnel callbacks.

The error function, declared in the super class Listener, will be called for all requests that returns with an error.
